link:labelLink.link:label: Tax Collection 4
International Dealings Transaction Control Tax Haven Countries Indicator

This indicates whether the entity has the ability or expectation to control transactions involving funds, property, assets or investments with certain countries specified as being tax jurisdictions of interest.

A choice of TRUE/FALSE values. true = The entity has the ability or expectation to control transactions with certain countries specified as being tax jurisdictions of interest. false = The entity does not have the ability or expectation to control transactions with certain countries specified as being tax jurisdictions of interest.
International Dealings Transactions With Tax Haven Countries Indicator
This indicates whether the entity has had transactions involving funds or property with certain countries specified as being tax jurisdictions of interest.

A choice of TRUE/FALSE values. true = The entity has had transactions involving funds or property with certain countries specified as being tax jurisdictions of interest. false = The entity has not had transactions involving funds or property with certain countries specified as being tax jurisdictions of interest.
